column5: Any bod=y been out on lake simcoe today ? .  Whats it like out there ,I'd like to get out of the house and do some fishing before it gets to late . Bay cam looks ok , winds dieing down .
You offer me fish and you haven't even caught them yet? I'll take 6 jumbos and a laker please.
6 jumbos i can do , the laker i have'nt a clue how to catch one ..................
Holy man , you ok ...........all you had to do was just look
I went for a drive by this morning, I think bigger anchors are in order, everybody was moving with the waves at a pretty good clip.
The corn was so loud,I couldnt hear the foot steps.
Glad i stayed in then but i am going to check again in the early morning and see if i can get out for a bit . Thanks every one .
